INSERT INTO `post` VALUES (1,'Insert Update Delete using Stored Procedure in Mysql and PHP - 1','In Video we have learn how to fetch data from database and Insert data to database using stored procedure in Mysql and PHP. Part 2 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qkN-LLStTdU Part 3 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dY_AhFsg6vM','Webslesson','2018-11-25 04:00:00','insert-update-delete-using-stored-procedure-in-mysql-and-php-1.jpg'),(2,'Insert Update Delete using Stored Procedure in Mysql and PHP - 2','In this Video we have to learn how to fetch single data from database and display data in form using stored procedure and update that data using stored procedure in MySql and PHP.','Webslesson','2018-11-26 21:00:00','insert-update-delete-using-stored-procedure-in-mysql-and-php-2.jpg'),(3,'Insert Update Delete using Stored Procedure in Mysql and PHP - 3 ','In this Video we have to learn how to delete single data from database using stored procedure and update that data using stored procedure in MySql and PHP.','Webslesson','2019-01-27 06:00:00','insert-update-delete-using-stored-procedure-in-mysql-and-php-3.jpg'),(4,'Auto Refresh Div Content Using jQuery and AJAX','How to do Auto Load and Refresh  Div every Seconds with jQuery and Ajax. So today I needed content in a div to refresh every seconds, so I used AJAX shorthand method .load() and setInterval() and then simply sets a call for the data every seconds. So every second div content will refresh automatically.','Webslesson','2018-11-30 22:00:00','auto-refresh-div-content-using-jquery-and-ajax.jpg'),(5,'How to generate simple random password in php?','For Generating random password in php I am using two string function. First is str_shuffle function and second is substr function.','Webslesson','2018-12-03 10:00:00','how-to-generate-simple-random-password-in-php.jpg'),(6,'Rename uploaded image in php with upload validation','In this video we learn how to upload image file, rename uploaded file, file upload validation like file is selected or not, file is with proper extension or not, size of file etc.','Webslesson','2018-12-03 03:00:00','rename-uploaded-image-in-php-with-upload-validation.jpg'),(7,'How to check Username availability using php, Ajax, Jquery and Mysql','In this video, we are going to learn how to check username available or not using php, mysql, Ajax and Jquary. If you want to restrict duplicate username then this video will helpful to you. http://www.webslesson.info/2016/02/how-to-check-username-availability-in.html','Webslesson','2018-12-05 19:00:00','how-to-check-username-availability-using-php-ajax-jquery-and-mysql.jpg'),(8,'How To Insert Data Using Stored Procedure In Php Mysql','In this video, we will learn how to call stored procedures using PHP. Stored procedures can increase website performance and decrease database access traffic.','Webslesson','2018-12-05 17:00:00','how-to-insert-data-using-stored-procedure-in-php-mysql.jpg'),(9,'How to merge two PHP JSON Array','In this video we are going to learn about how to merge two or more JSON array.','Webslesson','2018-12-05 03:00:00','how-to-merge-two-php-json-array.jpg'),(10,'How to check Multiple value exists in an Array in PHP','In this video I show you how to check multiple value exists or not in php array. Because for checking single value we can use in_array() function but there no php function for checking multiple value in php array. So I make this custom array function for checking multiple value in php array. This my function.\r\n\r\nfunction multiple_in_array($search, $source)\r\n{\r\nreturn (count(array_intersect($search, $source)) == count($search));\r\n}','Webslesson','2018-12-07 21:00:00','how-to-check-multiple-value-exists-in-an-array-in-php.jpg'),(11,'Create Simple Image using PHP','Hello Friends today we learn how to create simple Image using PHP GD Library. This type of generating dynamic image using php can be useful for many purpose e.g. Captcha Code Image http://www.webslesson.info/2016/01/cre